### 5.4 CRITICAL: No scroll on page load

The `activateEra()` function must NOT scroll on initial load:

```javascript
// WRONG — causes page to scroll to detail panel on load:
setTimeout(() => activateEra(0), 150);

// CORRECT — highlight only, no scroll:
function activateEra(idx, noScroll) {
  // ... update tabs, panels, block highlights ...
  if (noScroll) return;           // ← exit before scrollIntoView
  // ... scrollIntoView calls only for user clicks ...
}
